job_name = "BAHL"
description = "A HARMONY mortality-stats auditor who found a discrepancy, a ward dying off the network faster than it was dying for real, and was murdered for asking about it. He wakes Off-Network with the brand already ticking, and a write-key the system never quite managed to revoke. Silent, level, still believing a record, and a life, can be made true."
